description: Erection of part 6, part 10 and part 13 storey building comprising 134 residential units with ancillary facilities and parking (Class C3), flexible commercial floorspace (Class A1-A3, B1, D2) and all other incidental works. (Summary)
decision_conditions:
The development hereby permitted shall be begun no later than the  expiration of three years from the date of this permission.

Reason: In order to comply with the requirements of Section 91 of the Town and Country Planning Act 1990.
